{
  "stem": "18186.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 152,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We-- Everybody had to work the government.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 152,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Not private.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 153,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, that's when the-- the Russians were-- were-- left the-- the-- my town, Stepan, and the German came, we stayed a little-- a very short time in our own homes.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 153,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then they created the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 153,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And every--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 154,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Exactly, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 154,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think it was the-- the late '40s or early '41.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 155,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The ghetto was-- was located where the shul was, where the temple was.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 155,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they put fence all around, very high fence.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 155,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was, like, about, I would say, about two, three small streets.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 155,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "All the--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 156,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, all the Jewish people from town and from out of town, like, some close, really just then a few families were brought in.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 157,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the synagogue became-- no-- no more synagogue.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 157,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They keep-- in the synagogue, I think, they were keeping the potatoes and they cooked the food there because we used to get-- we-- every day we went for-- for our, our lunch or our dinner or whatever.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 157,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they gave us soup everyday.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 157,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This-- so everyone had a-- a little bit of soup.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 158,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 158,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And a little bread.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 159,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was it?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 159,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Every day.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 159,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 160,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 160,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 161,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What we did, we came home.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 161,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We ate it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 161,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was all-- the potatoes always were frozen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 161,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we ate was never, like, sweet.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 161,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When they are frozen, they are sweet, and they smelled.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 161,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But for us, we didn't have anything else to eat.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 161,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's what we ate.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 162,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, they were cooked.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 162,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They cooked this.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 163,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Jewish people actually cooked them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 163,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They put the people to work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 163,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they cooked what they had, what they gave-- what they gave them to cook.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 164,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I was in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 164,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had to leave our house, and we went into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
